column5: Looking for a spot on eagle with a American plan with your own boat.

Check out Birch Dale Lodge on the West arm. I have been going there since 2007 and I take my own boat and do the dinner plan. The food is great and you pick off the menu every night no set menu. I seem to gain weight every year I go there. It is about as good as it can get as far as I am concerned. The owner is top notch, the fellow fishermen I have met have been great and the cabins are clean and comfortable, they even built a new cabin over the winter.
Mrmusky14, I sent you a PM
+1 and back at you!! your group is awesome. See ya in August.
